sequenceDiagram
    participant Person as "User"
    participant Front as "Browser"
    participant Back as "PHP Backend"
    participant DB as "MySQL"

    Person->>Front: Enter email & password
    Front->>Back: POST /index.php?route=login
    Back->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE email=?
    DB->>Back: user row
    Back->>Back: verify password (hash check)
    Back->>Front: redirect to dashboard
    Front->>Person: Dashboard page